00:13:03.988 --> 00:13:08.797
position vector,
then r cross v is going to be

00:13:08.797 --> 00:13:10.740
constant,
which means that the motion

00:13:10.740 --> 00:13:13.409
will be in an plane,
and you will sweep area at a

00:13:13.409 --> 00:13:16.709
constant rate.
So now, that is not in itself a

00:13:16.709 --> 00:13:19.960
